{
  "stem": "1029.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it's just the feeling we had was from behind those darkened windows that we could feel their eyes, you know, watching us as we were going.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a long trek.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was cold, I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I remember it was-- it was weird because I expected regular cars that you sit in, you know, with third class, second class, first class.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this was cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember, in my eyes-- I mean, I asked my mother, why?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What's happening?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and she wasn't-- she was also shocked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I just-- Did you know that these were the cars that you were going to be loaded onto?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they just started loading us up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they just pushed us in, you know, like in a-- like, you know, in one of those-- you know, you see those Japanese subway, you know, scenes, you know, where the people are crowding in, and these-- and these people, these officials are pushing them into it.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was the same thing with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe 50, maybe 60.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was no place to sit, no place to do this or that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't so bad, because it's-- you know, this trip wasn't so long.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It went just to Szeged, you know, to this distribution camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't know where we were going to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But thank god, it didn't go too long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know it maybe went maybe about 12 hours or 16 hours or who knows?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no water, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was our first taste of terror, of--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--of being uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
